text: Lauren Felice Collins (born August 29, 1986) is a Canadian actress. She acts in both movies and television. She started acting in 1998. Between 2001 and 2008, she played Paige Michalchuk on Degrassi: The Next Generation. She played a Host in 1 Girl 5 Gays. In 2002, she won a Young Artist Award for her performance in Degrassi: The Next Generation. Collins was born in the Thornhill area of the Greater Toronto Area, Ontario. ==References== Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Ontario Category:Canadian child actors Category:Canadian movie actors Category:Canadian television actors
